title: Cozy newly remodeled lake view house! Great for entertaining!!
posting_body: ['Two brand new bathrooms with all new fixtures, a fully remodeled kitchen with Kitchen Aid appliances, new furnace and HVAC unit, brand new water softener system, wood burning fireplace, original hardwood floors.', 'New washer and dryer, reverse osmosis filtered water system.', 'Fireplace is TV ready with mounts already installed.', 'Deck with partial lake view.', '5 car heated garage with work table area, water utility sink.', 'Extra side garage door access to patio.', 'Quiet, wooded 1/2 acre lot.', 'Lots of areas for gardening.', 'Five minute walk to Old Log Cabin, the best restaurant in Forest Lake, for dinner and drinks!', "Three minute drive to Forest Lake boat launch, 15 minute drive to St. Croix River boat launch (William O'Brian State Park), 5 minutes to Big Marine boat launch, 20 minutes to Stillwater.", '35 mins to Downtown Minneapolis.']
